---
// src/pages/engineering/index.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Engineering Portfolio | Amir Aghabiglou">

  <div class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-300 flex-grow w-full py-12 selection:bg-cyan-900 selection:text-cyan-50">
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">

      <header class="mb-20 border-b border-slate-800 pb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400 tracking-wide">
          SYSTEMS_ARCHITECTURE // ML_OPS
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Applied AI Engineering
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          Designing and deploying end-to-end training pipelines for large-scale models. Specializing in HPC infrastructure, PyTorch, and hybrid Machine Learning architectures.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="mb-24">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-mono tracking-widest text-slate-500 uppercase mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-slate-700"></span> Core Competencies
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-colors group">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Model Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Transformer Architectures, Large Vision Models (5Kx5K), Deep Unfolding Models (R2D2), and Edge-Optimized Small Language Models.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-colors group">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Supervised Fine-Tuning (SFT), Low-Rank Adaptation (LoRA), 4-bit GGUF Quantization, Model Pruning, and Distillation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-colors group">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">HPC Cluster Scheduling (Slurm, PBS), Docker Containerization, CI/CD Actions, and Data Drift Monitoring (PSI).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-sm font-mono tracking-widest text-slate-500 uppercase mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-slate-700"></span> Systems & Architectures
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-12">

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan-900/10 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Electricity Theft Detection via Hybrid SLM</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                  A production-ready ML system addressing the token-inflation weaknesses of naive LLM approaches. Extracted 700+ statistical features via TSFRESH, utilized Isolation Forests for anomaly detection, and deployed a 4-bit quantized Phi-3 model as a reasoning engine.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">PyTorch</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">XGBoost</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">FastAPI</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">Docker</span>
                </div>
                <a href="https://github.com/amiraghabiglou/electricity-theft-detection" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-cyan-50 transition-colors">
                  Inspect Repository Source &rarr;
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-900/10 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Decoupled SLM Pipeline for Building Energy Profiling</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                  Engineered an isolated XGBoost microservice to interpret 8 architectural features for numerical regression, bypassing tabular hallucination issues. Orchestrated via FastAPI to a TinyLlama (1.1B) instance, utilizing Outlines to strictly constrain outputs to a predefined JSON schema.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">XGBoost</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">TinyLlama 1.1B</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">Outlines</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">FastAPI</span>
                </div>
                <a href="https://github.com/amiraghabiglou/energy-building-advisor" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
                  Inspect Repository Source &rarr;
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
             <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-900/10 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
             <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
              <div class="flex-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">R2D2: High-Dynamic Range LVMs</h3>
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold rounded border border-indigo-500/30">v2.0</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                  Engineered a Residual-to-Residual DNN series for massive-scale radio interferometry imaging. The architecture utilizes a hybrid structure bridging Plug-and-Play (PnP) algorithms with a learned Matching Pursuit algorithm, deploying U-Net and U-WDSR core networks.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                  Built end-to-end in PyTorch utilizing Non-Uniform Fast Fourier Transform (NUFFT) operators for high-resolution, super-resolved outputs, effectively overcoming standard optimization bottlenecks in terabyte-scale data regimes.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">PyTorch</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">NUFFT</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">U-WDSR / U-Net</span>
                  <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono text-cyan-400">HPC / Slurm</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                  <a href="https://github.com/basp-group/R2D2-RI" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-cyan-50 transition-colors">
                    View Source Repo &rarr;
                  </a>
                  <a href="https://basp-group.github.io/BASPLib/R2D2.html" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors ring-1 ring-slate-700">
                    BASPLib Project Page
                  </a>
                  <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.02554" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors ring-1 ring-slate-700">
                    Read ApJS Paper
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>